query.sfwSql: select sm.DISPLAY_MESSAGE,sm.SEVERITY_ID,sm.SEVERITY_VALUE, spabe.* from SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY_ERROR spabe WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY spab WITH(NOLOCK) on spabe.PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY_ID = spab.PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY_ID join SGT_RELATIONSHIP spb WITH(NOLOCK) on spab.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID join SGS_MESSAGES sm WITH(NOLOCK) on sm.MESSAGE_ID = spabe.MESSAGE_ID where spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = @PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID and spab.STATUS_VALUE <> 'INAC'

select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and ((BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID And BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID <> 0) OR (BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID = @BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID And BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID <> 0))
select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID = @BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID
Select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID
Select * from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID
select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID=@DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID
select * from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID = @DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID
select * from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID

IF((Select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where SGT_RELATIONSHIP.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and SGT_RELATIONSHIP.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = (select PERSON_ID from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID))>0) ( select (SGT_PERSON.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SGT_PERSON.LAST_NAME)as fullname ,SGT_PERSON.PERSON_ID,RELATIONSHIP_VALUE from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) left join SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) on SGT_PERSON.PERSON_ID = SGT_RELATIONSHIP.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID where SGT_RELATIONSHIP.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID =(select PERSON_ID from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID =@MPI_PERSON_ID) and SGT_RELATIONSHIP.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID ) else ( select (SGT_PERSON.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SGT_PERSON.LAST_NAME)as fullname ,PERSON_ID,'' 'RELATIONSHIP_VALUE' from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID )

IF((Select COUNT(*) from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where SGT_RELATIONSHIP.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and SGT_RELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID = (select PERSON_ID from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID))>0) ( select (SGT_PERSON.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SGT_PERSON.LAST_NAME)as fullname ,SGT_PERSON.PERSON_ID,RELATIONSHIP_VALUE from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) Right join SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) on SGT_PERSON.PERSON_ID = SGT_RELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID where SGT_RELATIONSHIP.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID = (select PERSON_ID from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID =@MPI_PERSON_ID) and SGT_RELATIONSHIP.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID ) else ( select (SGT_PERSON.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SGT_PERSON.LAST_NAME)as fullname ,PERSON_ID ,'' 'RELATIONSHIP_VALUE' from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID )
SELECT DATE_OF_BIRTH FROM SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID
SELECT MARITAL_STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID
select * from SGS_CODE_VALUE WITH(NOLOCK) where CODE_ID = 6000 and DATA1 = @DATA1

SELECT FIRST_NAME + ' ' + LAST_NAME AS SPOUSEFULLNAME , SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH SPOUSEDOB, SCV.DESCRIPTION AS SPOUSENAMEPREFIX, SP.Gender_Value AS SpouseGender FROM SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR WITH(NOLOCK) ON sp.Person_ID = sr.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN sgs_code_value SCV WITH(NOLOCK) ON SCV.CODE_ID = SP.NAME_PREFIX_ID AND SCV.CODE_VALUE = SP.NAME_PREFIX_VALUE WHERE SR.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE = 'SPOU' AND SR.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID
select DATE_OF_MARRIAGE from sgt_relationship where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID

SELECT top(1) BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP R WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND RELATIONSHIP_VALUE='SPOU' AND DATEADD(YY,1,R.DATE_OF_MARRIAGE) < GETDATE() ORDER BY R.DATE_OF_MARRIAGE DESC

select FIRST_NAME , LAST_NAME ,MIDDLE_NAME,NAME_PREFIX_VALUE,SSN from SGT_PERSON SP join SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR on sp.Person_ID = sr.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID where SR.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE = 'SPOU' and SR.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

select top(1) sp.*,BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID from sgt_person sp join sgt_relationship R on sp.person_id = R.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID WHERE R.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND RELATIONSHIP_VALUE='SPOU' ORDER BY R.DATE_OF_MARRIAGE DESC

SELECT top(1) BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP R WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and (BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID) AND RELATIONSHIP_VALUE='SPOU' AND DATEADD(YY,1,R.DATE_OF_MARRIAGE) < @DATE_OF_DEATH ORDER BY R.DATE_OF_MARRIAGE DESC

select PERSON_ID,FIRST_NAME ,LAST_NAME from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID in (select PERSON_ID from SGT_RELATIONSHIP WITH(NOLOCK) where BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID) and DATE_OF_DEATH is not NULL

select PERSON_ID,FIRST_NAME , LAST_NAME from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID in (select PERSON_ID from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) where ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID = @ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID and DRO_STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNLD')
SELECT * FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE BENEFECIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFECIARY_PERSON_ID and BENEFECIARY_OF_PERSON_ID = @BENEFECIARY_OF_PERSON_ID

select SR.RELATIONSHIP_ID,sr.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE from SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR join SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD on SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID=sbad.JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID join SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA on Sr.PERSON_ID=SPA.PERSON_ID where SPA.PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and sbad.JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID= @Beneficiary_person_id

select DIST_PERCENT from SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY SPAB join SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR on SPAB.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID=SR.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID where SR.PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID=@BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID and PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=@PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID
select RELATIONSHIP_VALUE from SGT_RELATIONSHIP where PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID= @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID
SELECT RELATIONSHIP_VALUE FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP WHERE PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID AND BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID=@BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID
select * from SGT_RELATIONSHIP where BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID=@DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID or DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID = @DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID or BENEFICIARY_OF = @DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID

select SPAB.*,SR.*, SPA.PLAN_ID from SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR left outer JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY SPAB ON SR.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = SPAB.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID left outer JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPAB.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID where SR.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and (BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID <> 0 or DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID <> 0)

select DATE_OF_DEATH from SGT_PERSON where person_id= (select TOP(1)SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID from SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR where SR.PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and SR.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE='SPOU' AND SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID IS NOT NULL)
